{"tid":2042542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果：BBC調查︰逾千「五毛」疫情期間狂發反美、香港抗爭假消息","createTime":"2020-05-30T01:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T09:57:55.000Z","uid":1654,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"321c956fe95048aa9d2f0832d03cf0ff0c98e9a6","tid":2042542,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T01:23:36.000Z","msg":"英國廣播公司（BBC）調查發現，逾1,200個虛假或盜用別人身份的親中賬戶，在Facebook、Twitter、YouTube等社交網發放有關武漢肺炎、香港民主運動的虛假負面訊息，又會吹捧及讚揚中共的「功蹟」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200529&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=60990155\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200529%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D60990155&d=MUobR5x4uSQxHz8Khhk%2FvDC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=2d3064f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200529%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D60990155&h=633ea89c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200529&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=60990155</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n儘管。。。。。。。。。假賬戶確實與去年被Facebook和Twitter刪除、源於中國並獲國家支持的網絡行動非常相似。就以Twitter一個賬戶「Joker1999」為例，。。。。。。<br />\n這些賬戶主要發放批評美國處理武漢肺炎疫情不力、香港民主運動的負面消息，同時又攻擊正在逃亡的中國富豪郭文貴。2014年郭文貴。。。。。。。。。<br />\n大部份賬戶在。。。。。。BBC發現逾1,000多個Twitter賬戶、53個Facebook專頁，關注者不足10萬；61個Facebook賬戶及187個YouTube頻道總共只有約1萬個訂閱者。自BBC向Facebook、Twitter、YouTube舉報這些賬戶後，大部份已經刪除。<br />\n社交網分析公司Graphika今年初亦揭發。。。。。。。營造出很多網民支持中國政府的假象，「但手法不老練，相對業餘」。尼莫估計BBC發現的這些賬戶。。。。。。。。。可能隸屬於「Spamouflage Dragon」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200529&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=60990155\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200529%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D60990155&d=MUobR5x4uSQxHz8Khhk%2FvDC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=2d3064f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200529%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D60990155&h=633ea89c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200529&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=60990155</a>"},{"pid":"71b96ddab8babefaa4e5a51ee4ea49d8cd01e2e7","tid":2042542,"uid":12628,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T01:52:33.000Z","msg":"舉報5毛，人人有責"},{"pid":"8b43a0738fd2fdc7ed97ec3aea979bd292f69c9f","tid":2042542,"uid":94360,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T01:55:51.000Z","msg":"5毛不斷分裂國家<br />\n罪該萬死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d5c232fa1e8416e24af249e154293e79c96739","tid":2042542,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T01:56:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e264ff42d844a61120a3e78b79c40e88b88e792","tid":2042542,"uid":1654,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T01:58:54.000Z","msg":"五毛網軍 唯一死刑"},{"pid":"d1a10ffa772614e5cfbcddb0a4d125382f33e6a0","tid":2042542,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T02:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a669a948dc6d364f16038133e209774a2487912","tid":2042542,"uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T02:01:37.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港都好多五毛啦<br />\n你地唔識用不推文<br />\n呢一世都會比五毛狗當狗咁撚</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/u1d7T2k.png\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/f0PLEg5.png\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mfMm0Hr.